lines.text: someone told me i should take
caution when it comes to love
and you were strong and i was not
you have gone and so effortlessly
you can go ahead tell them
tell them all i know now
shout it from the roof tops
write it on the sky line
all we had is gone now
tell them what i hoped would be

paragraphs.text: i remember years ago someone told me i should take caution when it comes to love i did, i did and you were strong and i was not my illusion, my mistake i was careless, i forgot i did
and now all is done there is nothing to say you have gone and so effortlessly you have won you can go ahead tell them
tell them all i know now shout it from the roof tops write it on the sky line all we had is gone now
tell them i was happy and my heart is broken all my scars are open tell them what i hoped would be impossible, impossible impossible, impossible
